I love stand up comedy & Arnez J is one of my favorite comedians.  When he performs, you will not be able to sit through his routine without crying laughing. He's a very funny comedian. This is from when he won his on standup segment on Comic View which is about 50 min. OMG, some of the things he does physically is so darn funny. If you're having a not so good day, WATCH this dvd, it will definitely cheer you up.
love all comic view dvds. i am trying to collect all of them.  this one is great.  i waited a while to find this one.
